44:54.600 --> 44:57.000
So we're going to go
for a jog in Central Park.

44:57.360 --> 45:00.760
We're heading uphill now, and
just when we're about to get to the top,

45:00.920 --> 45:03.240
we can almost
see the Waldorf Plaza.

45:03.560 --> 45:06.000
It's snowing really lightly.
When I talk to Glenn,

45:06.360 --> 45:07.960
I can feel him listening.

45:08.760 --> 45:10.120
Oh, hey Dad.

45:10.200 --> 45:11.760
She's not here anymore, David.

